<TEXT>
<P>
I have stopped watching "Married . . . With Children" since it has become 
extremely sleazy. Please don't insult our intelligence with your canned 
laughter after every dumb sexual innuendo is made. 
</P>
<P>
Joan Shelstad, 
</P>
<P>
Manhattan Beach 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Letter to the Editor 
</P>
