<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE BIG MIX 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
It's great that clubs such as Florentine Gardens attract an interracial crowd. 
But if you're not beautiful, a great dancer or wearing the latest clothes, 
forget it. These are showing-off places, and the people they attract are vapid, 
air-headed trendies. 
</P>
<P>
TAMMY LYN SMITH 
</P>
<P>
Santee, Calif. 
