THE BIG MIX 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Don Snowden's article on ethnic radio failed to mention KPCC, FM 89.3. Among 
our ethnic broadcasts are the "Sancho" show, which celebrates Los Angeles' 
Mexican heritage; "Rhythm &amp; Blues Times Capsule" and "Rhapsody in Black," 
which chronicle black music; "Echoes of Greece," "Polish/American Show," 
"German/American Show," "European Music Box," "Asian Hour" and "Ebony '89." 
</P>
<P>
RENE ENGEL, KPCC 
</P>
<P>
Assistant Program Director 
</P>
