<P>
We recognize the complaints against cultural institutions, which sometimes 
frustrate rather than encourage working artists ("A Theater of Cultural 
Diversity?" by Victor Valle). But our experience with Plaza de la Raza has been 
positive. As an emerging comedy troupe, we asked for Plaza's support; it found 
merit in our work and gave us access to their fine rehearsal facilities. 
</P>
