<P>
Book Review 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA021989-0057 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 20524 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
February 19, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
