<HEADLINE>
<P>
GORBACHEV AND TRUST 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
A front-page article ("Survey Shows Change in Cold War Thinking" on Jan. 24) 
declared that Gorbachev was rated more favorably than President Bush in a Times 
Orange County Poll. 
</P>
<P>
I live in Orange County and nobody asked my opinion. The only list that 
Gorbachev appears on of mine is the one entitled, "People I Least Trust." He's 
not even No. 1 on that list. He follows a close second -- after the news media! 
</P>
<P>
BRENDA HESTER 
</P>
<P>
Garden Grove 
</P>
