<P>
COUNCIL SETS BEAUTIFICATION AWARDS DATE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Los Angeles Business Council will present its 19th annual beautification 
awards April 3 to owners, contractors, architects and landscape architects for 
new and remodeled projects. 
</P>
<P>
Awards will be given in the following categories: community, institutional or 
public project; commercial high-rise, mid-rise or low-rise. Residential: 
single- and multifamily; landscaping; commercial and residential. 
</P>
<P>
To be eligible, building projects must have been completed in 1988. Landscape 
projects must have been completed in 1987 or 1988. 
</P>
<P>
The deadline for submissions is March 10. 
</P>
