GEORGE; RACIAL RELATIONS -- LOUISIANA; POLITICAL CAMPAIGNS; REPUBLICAN PARTY 
(LOUISIANA); METAIRE (LA); POLITICAL CANDIDATES; POLITICAL ENDORSEMENTS; TREEN, 
JOHN 
</P>
