UNITED STATES -- IMMIGRATION; JEWS -- USSR; ARMENIANS -- USSR; REFUGEES -- 
USSR; SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA -- FEDERAL AID; VISAS; USSR -- EMIGRATION 
</P>
